_sText:
Hope you like it:

Change log:

-Fixed trigger Push values
-Fixed over-extended brushes interfering with trigger_push
-Changed skybox and lighting
-Changed ending ramp to make it easier to surf
-Fixed Bridge setup and added new features
-Changed Bridge wood textures
-Added more trigger_teleports to stop cheating and stop you from dying if you fall off the map
-Fixed weapon manager to start with 9mm, 7.62mm, and .45 ACP ammo
-Fixed other small problems and bugs
